            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/30/meet-janet-cowell-the-north-carolina-treasurer-desperately-pushing-to-keep-criminal-public-pension-fees-secret/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Meet Janet Cowell – The North Carolina Treasurer Desperately Pushing to Keep Criminal Public Pension Fees Secret"><span>4</span> Comments</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/alternative-investments/" rel="tag">alternative investments</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/bloomberg/" rel="tag">Bloomberg</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/david-sirota/" rel="tag">David Sirota</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/ponzi-finance/" rel="tag">ponzi finance</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/private-equity/" rel="tag">Private Equity</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/yves-smith/" rel="tag">Yves Smith</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/30/meet-janet-cowell-the-north-carolina-treasurer-desperately-pushing-to-keep-criminal-public-pension-fees-secret/#comments">4</a> 
