            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/07/03/chinese-malls-waive-rents-due-to-soaring-vacancies/#respond" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Chinese Malls Waive Rents Due to Soaring Vacancies">Leave a comment</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/bloomberg/" rel="tag">Bloomberg</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/buy-to-rent/" rel="tag">Buy to Rent</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/china-collapse/" rel="tag">China collapse</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/china-ponzi/" rel="tag">China Ponzi</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/ghost-cities/" rel="tag">Ghost cities</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/ghost-malls/" rel="tag">Ghost malls</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/07/03/chinese-malls-waive-rents-due-to-soaring-vacancies/#comments">0</a> 
